description._content:
Page 34 of the 1919 Central Ontario telephone directory, showing numbers for Deseronto, the Maracle Telephone Line, the Perry Telephone Co., Tyendinaga Municipal Telephone Co. and the first page of telephone numbers for residents of Fenelon Falls.

The Deseronto numbers, residents, occupations and street addresses on this page are as follows:

56  Sharpe, A C  Garage & Livery  St. George
34  Spencer, S. W  Garage  Thomas
91  Stainton, Jos.  Furniture & Undertkr  St. George
100  Standard Bank of Canada  Office  Main
38  Standard Iron Co.  Office  Main
68  Standon, John  Residence  Main
17  Stewart House    Main
131  Stoddart, Miss M.S  Residence  St. George
88  Therrien, A  Grocer  Main
20  Vandervoort, Dr. E.D  Office & Residence  Mill
53  VanDusen, Howard  Residence  Stanley Ave.
41  Webster, H  Residence  Dundas
86  Wright, G. W  Residence  St. George

Scanned image donated by Susan Wright of the South Fredericksburg Heritage Committee.
